com.psddev.dari.util

Class AsyncConsumer<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.psddev.dari.util.Task
      • com.psddev.dari.util.AsyncConsumer<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Task>, Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AsyncDatabaseWriter, AsyncProcessor, AsyncStorageItemWriter

    public abstract class AsyncConsumer<E>
extends Task
    Background task that consumes all items from an input queue.

    Sub-classes must implement:

    • consume(E)

      Optionally, they can futher override:

      • beforeStart()
      • handleError(E, java.lang.Exception)
      • finished()
